t: "Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe wote njaggire a√±…ìe Mi e a√±…ìe mon heet…ìe ho…óon mberlo e mum en gilli te ko…ìe yeddu…ìe goongo gar…óo o e mon, ho…ìe njaltina nelaa…óo e onon sabu tan on ngoon…óanii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol Am e …óa…ìjude weluya am, ho…óon cuurtana…ìe kabaruuji juul…ìe ngam …ìe mbele mon, Mbe…óa anndi ko cuu…óoton e ko …ìanngi…óon, kala e mon ba…ó…óo …óuum o majji laawol peewngol"